@node bugs " MiXeRz -- KNOWN BUGS -- "

 I haven't managed to find a bug yet, runnning two remote nodes and a
couple more locals hasn't caused any damage (yet), so I presume that if any
problems accure, then it's your fault, but if the problem resumes then
contact me.

PS. Sometimes you might feel the process is a bit slow, but that's the code
itself that's slowing it down, I'm going to work on a better code which
will NOT be released, and if you want that code you can contact me for a
copy. (free)



