@node future " MiXeRz -- FUTURE MIXZ RELEASES -- "

 There won't be any more MIXZ releases for a while, as I will program
better versions of the scripts, and in a couple of days from the release
date of this collection there will be better scripts already made. However, I
won't release them, but if you want them just contact me, I want to see
just how many people liked this door.

Future Upgrades :

* Quicker Source
* More mixers
* smaller source



