@node ME " MiXeRz -- ABOUT THE AUTHOR -- "

 Well, after a long time without programing any scripts, I have to say that
these scripts are just the right sign for my comeback. I've been working on
scripts since January this year (98) though I've stopped after almost a
month because of school stuff and - for once - I had more than ten loggers
each day to my bbs! Hurrah! And it was quite amusing just watching users og
on and off (so much for the studying) .

Though, just two days back, I managed to spare sometime (from my holiday,
not school) to make these scripts, and now, I am addicted once again. I
will be making scripts all through this summer, possibly even more.



